net.sourceforge.waters.model.module

Interface ExpressionProxy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Proxy
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BinaryExpressionProxy, EnumSetExpressionProxy, EventListExpressionProxy, FunctionCallExpressionProxy, IdentifierProxy, IndexedIdentifierProxy, IntConstantProxy, LabelBlockProxy, PlainEventListProxy, QualifiedIdentifierProxy, SimpleExpressionProxy, SimpleIdentifierProxy, UnaryExpressionProxy
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryExpressionElement, EnumSetExpressionElement, EventListExpressionElement, ExpressionElement, FunctionCallExpressionElement, IdentifierElement, IndexedIdentifierElement, IntConstantElement, LabelBlockElement, PlainEventListElement, QualifiedIdentifierElement, SimpleExpressionElement, SimpleIdentifierElement, UnaryExpressionElement

    public interface ExpressionProxy
extends Proxy
    The base class of all expressions. This is the base class of all expressions that may occur in a module. This includes the expressions in package net.sourceforge.waters.model.expr as well as the special event list expressions (EventListExpressionProxy) that are specific to modules.
    Author:
    Robi Malik
